      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HEY YOU GUYS (6) was strongly fancied latest and proved too good with a 6 length win at this track in a handy 17.38. Awkwardly drawn but goes well over this trip. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to her credit. Will go close again if runs up to latest. DYNAMIC SUNNY (1) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (19.94) at Angle Park behind Grand Chief in a Grade 2/3/4. Stalked the pace but found the line strongly. Has a strong record out of this box with eight wins and a minor placing from nine starts. Expecting another good run. CHEQUES TO BURN (4) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when fifth at this track over 305m behind One More Button (17.81) in a OPEN. Was in the money prior to that. Form from her last run is proving strong. In the mix. MISTER CADILLAC (2) was in the money two back in a Grade 2/3/4 at this track then jumped from a squeeze draw last time and was not far away when second (23.33) over 400m at this track.",
